{"tid":1920060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜指市政府正規劃「香港村」歡迎港人移民高雄","createTime":"2020-03-11T08:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T15:50:46.000Z","uid":85745,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf6631c1168504d7e1ae2a8c6ccefdb1f99f34f","tid":1920060,"uid":85745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:05:59.000Z","msg":"在台灣，高雄市長韓國瑜透露，市政府正在規劃「香港村」，等疫情過後要宣傳高雄，歡迎香港及馬來西亞人移民。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜說，無論是新型肺炎抑或登革熱，都不能忽視，形容全世界華人的眼睛都在看高雄，市政府正思考未來如何讓貨出去、人進來，讓觀光客快樂來高雄，亦讓高雄的東西源源不絕賣出去。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜說，只要香港人願意移民，坐飛機90分鐘就可以回家，希望港人移民首選高雄，亦歡迎馬來西亞人來。<br />\n<br />\nsource: RTHK news<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513774-20200311.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513774-20200311.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0sttRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=c1afd0df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513774-20200311.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5159aa99\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513774-20200311.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3f8f340760c8e99993395dcfa88bf0f93920efd8","tid":1920060,"uid":85745,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:09:57.000Z","msg":"高雄發大財原本唔係靠大陸人, 而係打算靠香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3806aa68e685c9d6b5030d4d28aeecfd9fe1bb29","tid":1920060,"uid":302151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:10:26.000Z","msg":"宇智波"},{"pid":"53816076f333c35c9d037905c982fc2ddd9a8225","tid":1920060,"uid":66945,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:10:41.000Z","msg":"只歡迎藍絲?"},{"pid":"f41a21fe4a178e740b89f4c71521a7fb5cc87ea5","tid":1920060,"uid":109780,"like":0,